  "texts": [
    "The voices of absent people can have incredible control over us.",
    "Imagine being a child and taking a cookie from the forbidden cookie jar.",
    "In those moments of solitude, you are likely to hear the voice of a physically absent caretaker scolding you.",
    "As a result, you either abandon your plan and leave the cookie in the jar, or you take the cookie and go against your caretakers' wishes.",
    "In both scenarios, the voices of your absent caretakers have a distinct power over your actions."
  ],
